on rotten tomatoes it's easy to search for someone and then see a list of everything they've been in
you can sort on year or rating

for an author it'd be:

title publication_year rating num_reviews

compare rating, num_reviews between goodreads and amazon
https://www.goodreads.com/search?q=mary+roach
https://www.amazon.com/s/ref=nb_sb_noss_2?url=search-alias%3Dstripbooks&field-keywords=mary+roach